14 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 70 O.S. 2021, Section 17-113, is
15 amended to read as follows:
16 Section 17-113. A. In determining annual increments for
17 teacher salaries and in computing Foundation Aid, time spent in
18 military service during a period of national emergency shall be
19 counted, not to exceed five (5) years prior to the current year. No
20 more than five (5) years of such military service shall be used in
21 determining eligibility or benefits under the Teachers' Retirement
22 System.
23 B. For purposes of this section, the term "military service"
24 shall include the United States Air Force, Army, Coast Guard, Marine
